<a class='reflink' href='../3.dcf/3.1.dpapi.html#lemmacovers'>3.1.7</a>

<!-- 3.1.7 -->
<div class='toload lemma'>
	<p><span class='envidentifier'>Lemma 3.1.7</span>
	Suppose $\mathcal{A}$ is weakly regular, and let $A\subseteq\mathcal{A}$ and $b\in\mathcal{A}$. The following are equivalent:
	<ol class='arpar'>
		<li>
			$A$ is a cover of $b$.
		</li>
		
		<li>
			The closure of $\bigcup_{a\in A}[a\neq\theta]$ contains $\supp(b)$.
		</li>
	</ol>
	</p>
</div>